  {
    "english_title": "Psalms Introduction",
    "coptic_title": null,
    "arabic_title": "من المزامير",
    "title": "Psalms Introduction",
    "tbodies": [
      {
        "rows": [
          {
            "row-class": "text",
            "cells": [
              {
                "english": "The prayer of the third hour of this blessed day, we offer to Christ our King and our God, beseeching Him to forgive us our sins.",
                "arabic": "تسبحةُ الساعةِ الثالثةِ مِنَ النهارِ المبارَكِ، أقدِّمُها للمسيحِ ملكي وإلهي، وأرجوهُ أن يغفِرَ لي خطايايَ."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "row-class": "text",
            "cells": [
              {
                "english": "From the Psalms of our teacher David the prophet. May his blessings be upon us all. Amen.",
                "arabic": "مِنْ مزاميرِ مُعلِّمِنا داودَ النبي بركاتِهِ علينا. آمين."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
